Template.Name: Home Page
Template.Design:
<%@ Master Language="VB" MasterPageFile="/masterpages/ContentMaster.master" %> <asp:Content ContentPlaceHolderId="Meta" runat="server"> <meta name="Author" content="WhiteSpace Creative, http://www.whitespace-creative.com" /> <meta name="Designer" content="WhiteSpace Creative, http://www.whitespace-creative.com" /> </asp:Content>
<asp:Content ContentPlaceHolderId="Head" runat="server"> <link href="inc/style/home.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /> <script src="inc/js/home.js"></script> </asp:Content>
<asp:Content ContentPlaceHolderId="Body" runat="server"> <umbraco:Macro imageWidth="100" imageHeight="214" Alias="WSC.HomeFeature" runat="server" /> <umbraco:Macro title="News" myClass="news" maxNodes="3" source="1097" dateFormat="MM.dd.yyyy" Alias="WSC.NewsWidget" runat="server" /> <umbraco:Macro title="Events" myClass="events" maxNodes="3" source="1095" dateFormat="MM.dd.yyyy" Alias="WSC.EventWidget" runat="server" /> <umbraco:Macro maxNodes="3" random="1" imageWidth="100" imageHeight="100" Alias="WSC.Ads" runat="server" /> <umbraco:Macro title="Blog" myClass="blog" dateFormat="MM.dd.yyyy" summaryCount="150" maxNodes="3" source="1075" Alias="WSC.BlogWidget" runat="server" /> </asp:Content>
